# Privileged Identity/Access Management Lab

# Objective:
I implemented Privileged Identity Management by assigning eligible roles and enabling Just-In-Time activation for user access.

## Overview
This project demonstrates how privileged access is managed securely using Microsoft Entra ID PIM.

## Steps Implemented

 Explore PIM dashboard — roles, assignments, audit 
 Assign a user as Eligible for Network Administrator role 
 Configure role settings — approval, MFA, max duration 
 User submit request to activate the role with justification
 Approver reivew and approve an activation request for JIT access
 Export audit log as compliance evidence 

